data.comment: The first-half is just kicking off.

Throw-in for AIK in their own half.
Free kick Djurgarden.

A throw-in for the home team on the opposite half.

Glenn Nyberg signals a free kick to AIK in their own half.

Djurgarden's Emir Kujovic breaks free at Friends Arena. But the strike goes wide of the post.

Throw-in for Djurgarden close to the penalty box.

Free kick for AIK in their own half.

Corner awarded to AIK.

Thomas Lagerlof is making the team's fourth substitution at Friends Arena with Kevin Walker replacing Haris Radetinac.
Fredrik Ulvestad (Djurgarden) has been booked and must now be careful not to get a second yellow card.
